item.dc:creator: @yesimanub yesimanub
item.description:
@yesimanub wrote:

[quote=“zyle1992, post:4, topic:469062”][quote author=tyb97 link=topic=586100.msg4162034#msg4162034 date=1353217781]

An orphaned case means that it’s case outside the switch block.

What it should look like

switch (something) {
    case 1234:
        break;
}

What you have

switch (something) {
}
case 1234:
break;

Yeep…

@OP: To protect what, coordinates lol?
[/quote]

That’s the only thing I could think of. Perhaps he doesn’t want us to know the location of his Home location or PVP area.[/quote]

thanks
